l squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kozhemyakin, Oleg}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:People from Kryvyi Rih]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:FC Metallurg Lipetsk players]]\n[[Category:FC Lokomotiv Moscow players]]\n[[Category:FC Shinnik Yaroslavl players]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-midfielder-1995-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Eastern Slavic name|Andreyevich|Kozhemyakin}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| image = \n| name = Oleg Kozhemyakin\n| fullname = Oleg Andreyevich Kozhemyakin\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1995|5|30|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Kryvyi Rih]], [[Ukraine]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[FC Shinnik Yaroslavl]] \n| clubnumber = 8\n| youthyears1 = {{0|0000}}\u20132013 | youthclubs1 = SDYuSShOR-63 Smena Moscow\n| youthyears2 = 2013            | youthclubs2 = [[FC Lokomotiv Moscow]]\n| years1 = 2013\u20132014 | clubs1 = FC Kvazar Moscow                | caps1 =    | goals1 = \n| years2 = 2014\u20132017 | clubs2 = [[FC Metallurg Lipetsk]]        | caps2 = 72 | goals2 = 4\n| years3 = 2017\u20132018 | clubs3 = [[FC Lokomotiv-Kazanka Moscow]] | caps3 = 24 | goals3 = 1\n| years4 = 2018\u2013     | clubs4 = [[FC Shinnik Yaroslavl]]        | caps4 = 36 | goals4 = 0\n| pcupdate = 25 May 2019\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n'''Oleg Andreyevich Kozhemyakin''' ({{lang-ru|\u041e\u043b\u0435\u0433 \u0410\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0435\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u041a\u043e\u0436\u0435\u043c\u044f\u043a\u0438\u043d}}; born 30 May 1995) is a [[Russia]]n [[association football|football]] player who plays for [[FC Shinnik Yaroslavl]].\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his professional debut in the [[Russian Professional Football League]] for [[FC Metallurg Lipetsk]] on 2 August 2014 in a game against [[FC Arsenal-2 Tula]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian Professional Football League]]|url=http://www.pfl-russia.com/competitions/season-2014-2015/center/player.php?